# README.md

```markdown
# tempo-cli

A tiny command-line stopwatch and countdown timer.

## Install

    bun install
    bun link

## Usage

    tempo start            # start a stopwatch
    tempo count 5m         # count down 5 minutes
    tempo start --label "deep work"

Configuration lives in config/default.json. See the timer implementation in
the src/timer.ts file of this folder.
```

